out/ 2017 LGCT #5 Page]</ref> Winner: {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Rolf-Göran Bengtsson]] with horse Casall ASK<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/hamburg/results/1722/class-05-hamburg-2017-csi5-160m/ LGCT's Class 05: Hamburg 2017 CSI5* 1.60m Final Results Page]</ref> ** June 8–10: 2017 LGCT #6 in {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Cannes]]<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/cannes/info/about/ 2017 LGCT #6 Page]</ref> Winner: {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Álvarez Moya]] with horse Arrayan<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/cannes/results/1747/class-14-cannes-2017-csi5-160m-gp-lgct/ LGCT's Class 14: Cannes 2017 CSI5* 1.60m Final Results Page]</ref> ** June 23–25: 2017 LGCT #7 in {{MON}}<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/monaco/info/about/ 2017 LGCT #7 Page]</ref> Winner: {{flagicon|ITA}} Alberto Zorzi with horse Cornetto K<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/monaco/results/1758/class-10-monaco-2017-csi5-160-m/ LGCT's Class 10: Monaco 2017 CSI5* 1.60 m Final Results Page]</ref> ** June 30 – July 2: 2017 LGCT #8 in {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Paris]]<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/paris/info/about/ 2017 LGCT #8 Page]</ref> Winner: {{flagicon|FRA}} Julien Epaillard with horse Usual Suspect d'Auge<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/paris/results/1769/class-12-paris-2017-csi5-160m/ LGCT's Class 12: Paris 2017 CSI5* 1.60m Final Results Page]</ref> ** July 7 & 8: 2017 LGCT #9 in {{flagicon|POR}} [[Cascais]]-[[Estoril]]<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/cascais-estoril/info/about/ 2017 LGCT #9 Page]</ref> Winner: {{flagicon|ISR}} Danielle Goldstein with horse Lizziemary<ref>[https://www.globalchampionstour.com/events/2017/cascais-estoril/results/1782/class-04-cascais-estoril-2017-csi5-160m-grand-prix-lgct/ LGCT's Class 04: Cascais, Estoril 2017 CSI5* 1.60m Final Results Page]</ref> ** July 13–16: 2017 LGCT #10 in {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Chantilly, Oise]]<ref>[https://www.