se Darry Lou))<ref>[https://sprucemeadows.com/tournaments/media/1505003496356_817.pdf 2017 SM's BMO Nations Cup Final Results Page]</ref> ** Main event #2 -> The CP 'International' presented by Rolex ** Winner: {{flagicon|GER}} Philipp Weishaupt (with horse LB Convall)<ref>[https://sprucemeadows.com/tournaments/media/1505077585052_818.pdf 2017 SM's CP 'International' Results Page]</ref>
