{{Ref improve|date= November 2014}}
'''Aurland Stadion''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Aurlandsvangen]], [[Aurland]], [[Norway]]. Built in 1960, it received [[all-weather running track]] in 1985 and was last renovated in 1992. The track is {{convert|400|m|sp=us|0}} long and has four tracks.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.friidrett.no/anlegg/friidrettsanlegg/Documents/Aurland.pdf |title=Aurland |publisher=[[Norwegian Athletics Association]] |language=Norwegian |accessdate=9 December 2011 |archivedate=9 December 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/63o4o3EQv?url=http://www.friidrett.no/anlegg/friidrettsanlegg/Documents/Aurland.pdf |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref>

[[Sogndal Fotball]] played a home match at Aurland Stadion in 1998.<ref>{{cite news |title=Seriestarten i fare på Marienlyst |last=Bugge |first=Mette |work=[[Aftenposten]] |date=5 April 1998 |page=39 |language=Norwegian}}</ref>

