'''Khan Nasrullah Totakhail''' (born 1925) was an [[Afghanistan]] field hockey player, who competed at the [[1948 Summer Olympic Games]] and the [[1956 Summer Olympic Games]]. He played in all six matches in both Olympics.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/to/khan-nasrullah-totakhail-1.html Sports-Reference Profile]</ref>
