The '''RDS Cup''' is awarded annually by the [[Quebec Major Junior Hockey League]] to the overall [[Rookie of the Year (award)|Rookie of the Year]]. The Cup was known as the '''Molson Cup''' from 1991 to 1994, and the '''New Face Cup''' from 1994 to 1996, but is now sponsored by the French-language sports network [[Réseau des sports]] (RDS).
